    DURATION SHORT.

  PRIVATE SECTION.

    DATA mo_syntax_highlighter TYPE REF TO zcl_abapgit_syntax_highlighter.

    METHODS:
      setup,
      process_line  FOR TESTING,
      format_line   FOR TESTING,
      apply_style   FOR TESTING.

